      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Candidate A has a polished, professional tone, using formal language and a structured approach that suggests they understand corporate etiquette. Candidate B sounds very casual and uses slang, which might be perceived as unprofessional in a formal client-facing environment. While both candidates address the core issue, Candidate A's delivery is much more suitable for representing a company to clients.",
